Subject: [PATCH 0328/2066] arm64: renesas: add Salvator-X board support

upstream 1950fab0789111de4ba3406c6e93dc57e345d32c commit

Add initial board support for r8a7795 Salvator-X. At this point
only DEBUG0 and DEBUG1 serial ports are supported.

